Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.13,0:01:42.28,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:47.37,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Please grant...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:48.46,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,My wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:50.56,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like she's been resurrected!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:51.31,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.77,0:01:53.38,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:56.20,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,So Menma's come back to have her wish granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:58.25,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:02:00.47,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I think she's just my hallucination.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:03.53,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A hallucination? Like a fantasy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.53,0:02:05.14,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:07.10,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,So, is she here now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:08.74,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,No, right now she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:11.45,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Menma! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.45,0:02:11.96,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:13.36,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Or in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.91,0:02:16.44,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you? Let me see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:20.41,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I blurted out everything about Menma in the heat of the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:24.24,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't expect him to accept everything so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:18.86,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you over there? {said during Jinta's line}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.41,0:02:21.82,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.48,0:02:24.24,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Menma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.75,0:02:25.86,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,It's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.86,0:02:27.20,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.99,0:02:29.35,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Like I told you, she's just my...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:32.04,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty awesome man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:34.45,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:37.09,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:40.14,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,So you've been using this secret fort?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:43.24,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but only when I'm in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:44.10,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,In Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.10,0:02:47.77,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. All of those red circles mark places that I've visited.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:50.35,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see all kinds of different places in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.35,0:02:53.29,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,So I've been traveling using the money I saved from my part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.71,0:02:54.73,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,What about high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:57.59,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:59.71,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,On my last trip I went to Southeast Asia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.42,0:03:03.15,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Vietnamese chicks are so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:06.08,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan, you're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:09.37,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,He used to be tiny, and now he's gotten so huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:10.26,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,And like this, and like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:10.83,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:13.00,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,They're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:14.50,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed, have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:15.76,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:19.76,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,I've changed plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.76,0:03:21.46,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna take a cruise down to my jungle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:23.42,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's going to pop out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:23.43,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:24.80,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Right, we're getting way off topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:27.18,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,We were talking about Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:29.24,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Did you make her some kind of promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.24,0:03:31.02,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:36.86,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't she mention she wanted Desu Yo.'s autograph? {Desu Yo is a comedian apparently http://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%81%A7%E3%81%99%E3%82%88%E3%80%82}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:39.94,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think she'd rise from the grave for Desu Yo.?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:43.20,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,You know, maybe it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.62,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you, Kurimaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:11.71,Default,Old,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you some yogurt when we get home. Yogurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:13.36,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:24.64,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So Naruko, did you really go over to Yadomi's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:27.27,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:31.63,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,Having to deal with a hikikomori must suck. {leave shut-in as hikikomori? THERE'S A WIKI ENTRY SO IT'S COMMON ENGLISH}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:34.29,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,But, don't you feel that way sometimes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:34.67,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:40.54,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,You know, feeling like you don't want to do anything, not wanting to get out of bed in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.54,0:04:44.13,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes, I... actually, I often feel like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:48.10,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know what you mean. But I don't want to be compared to that loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:51.99,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably having a wet dream about you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:54.74,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That's so believable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.74,0:04:55.91,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,How creepy! {timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:05.34,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:06.61,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's an Oodai student.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:07.94,Default,Girl2,0000,0000,0000,,What a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:09.15,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:13.73,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:15.25,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:17.60,Default,Waitr,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:20.88,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuru...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:22.96,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Tsurumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:26.30,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! You forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:32.64,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:38.29,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,You should just ignore me during situations like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:43.30,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be embarrassed if anyone saw me talking to a girl from Mido High.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:46.03,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:47.86,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.05,0:05:51.14,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I went out of my way to bring that to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.14,0:05:52.38,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ask you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.90,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Stop it you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:59.83,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Anaru, Tsuruko, don't fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.97,0:05:57.45,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Since when were you so full of yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:59.83,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,You were always so timid as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.79,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,And you haven't changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:05.99,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,You were always easily influenced by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.99,0:06:09.82,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Those girls look like they can't keep their legs shut and you fit right in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:10.66,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Their legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:14.07,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you always used to imitate Meiko Honma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:20.24,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use a dead girl's name so lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:23.94,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Anaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:31.12,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,You still get upset when you say it yourself. You're so hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:32.94,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:37.40,Default,Tsuru,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:39.20,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:46.19,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:50.20,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.27,0:06:52.59,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,To be like Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:55.64,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,On that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:58.80,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:06:59.60,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:03.23,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,You like Menma, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:07.97,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,If only I hadn't spurred them on like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:08.65,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:10.91,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd like an ugly girl like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.21,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.05,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:32.65,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't, then things wouldn't have gone like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:47.45,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.90,0:07:53.30,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Anaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:06.22,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,When the froggie croaks, it's time to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.22,0:08:09.25,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,When the froggie croaks...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.40,0:08:16.43,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Where should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:24.35,Default,Bro,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:28.26,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Umm..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.26,0:08:29.44,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.01,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:38.58,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.05,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,What? Nokemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:44.46,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to criticize a customer for what he buys?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.45,0:08:49.27,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Which Nokemon do you want? Opal? Emerald?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:50.98,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:52.80,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaaa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.89,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Nokemon Gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:56.99,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,How many years ago did that come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:00.25,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Please sell it to me if you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.25,0:09:01.90,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, sell it to me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:04.11,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,What? A rare Nokemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.11,0:09:07.26,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Menma really wanted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:08.77,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,But she just couldn't find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.17,0:09:12.45,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, she did say something about Building Builder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:14.74,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Then that must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:17.48,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 4,571 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:21.67,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that pricey for a game that came out five years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:24.89,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you know that that's a fair price.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:28.00,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,There's a premium on this game since you can't find it anywhere anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:31.92,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.03,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:37.22,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Yadomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:43.57,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Thank you for your purchase.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:55.90,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, welcome back, Jinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.90,0:09:57.29,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:10:00.46,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Today I came up with a rather fabulous dish. {not sure; genba kara deta?}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:02.24,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So we're having fried meat for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.79,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:08.71,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you? That's not cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.85,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, how did it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.51,0:10:16.37,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Start off by picking one out of the three critters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:24.99,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Menma still hasn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:29.17,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,She's my stress manifesting itself as a hallucination.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:32.65,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,She shouldn't exist in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:34.59,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,But.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:37.40,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,But.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:13.27,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:15.91,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:26.48,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:29.51,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:34.54,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Yukiatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.95,0:11:35.97,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Po...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:37.92,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hisakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:40.94,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me Poppo like in the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:43.35,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,You're being so cold, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:45.88,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time anyone's called me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.20,0:11:47.88,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:50.15,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.15,0:11:53.65,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Menma's been resurrected over at Jintan's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.53,0:11:56.43,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Is he bringing that up again...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.43,0:11:57.44,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.54,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.82,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's he saying about Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:05.34,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! I saw him again for the first time in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:07.73,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,He's as awesome as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.73,0:12:10.27,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,What is he saying about Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:17.04,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... He called her an auditory hallucination? Or maybe a visual one?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:21.46,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not too sure, but apparently Menma wants him to grant her wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:32.43,Default,Jintan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap, I fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:34.85,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:39.69,Default,Jintan,0000,0000,0000,,Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:40.61,Default,Jintan,0000,0000,0000,,You came...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:45.14,Default,Jintan,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:47.90,Default,Jintan,0000,0000,0000,,Go take a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:50.06,Default,Jintan,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's still around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:56.30,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,You know Jintan, I tried to wash myself, but it just felt like air blowing at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:57.88,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I hate that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:12:59.42,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:04.26,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,You should pay a little more attention to the fact that you've matured.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.05,0:13:09.10,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you haven't matured all that much in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.54,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,In one place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:13.46,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:15.72,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Put on some clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:17.97,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:22.25,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? I get the feeling I've met you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:24.96,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:28.43,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Holy crap, Poppo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:31.87,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You're huge! Growth spurts are so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:31.87,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Poppo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:32.69,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.98,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Trading with friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:36.96,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Gollum. {gokuri; gokurin is apparently a pokemon, gokuri is jap for gollum, and maybe she's just making a swallowing sound because there's meat in front of her}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:38.14,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:42.05,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you get it when you trade Nokemon using a cable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:48.52,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! The meat's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.52,0:13:50.76,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's leftovers from last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:53.27,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm off to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:56.00,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Have a- Have a safe trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:14:00.80,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I'd completely forgotten. It makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:03.73,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Menma did say her wish can't come true without everyone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.19,0:14:05.49,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,It does sound right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.81,0:14:08.74,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing. How did you remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:10.46,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yukia...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.31,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what happened again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:14.50,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I saw an auditory hallucination, too.  {timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:16.98,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,You can't see auditory hallucinations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:18.34,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:19.88,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, so that's what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:22.90,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,So we need to get our hands on another Nokemon game.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:25.84,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone who might already have the game...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:33.31,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,She's definitely cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:43.13,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I hated my curly hair and glasses back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:46.28,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Menma, who had straight hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.45,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Menma, whom Jintan liked...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:52.80,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Anaru, let's get matching stickers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:53.69,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.69,0:14:56.20,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Here, isn't this cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:58.08,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:01.42,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.04,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:04.97,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:11.02,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I really liked her, but I also really hated her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.17,0:15:21.83,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Naruko, come down here for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:25.90,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a slave-driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.57,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,It's over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:28.30,Default,Jintan,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:29.61,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:32.68,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Anaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:38.37,Default,Jintan,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.44,0:15:41.58,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.58,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to play Nokemon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:44.92,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:49.61,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with acting like kids every once in a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:51.26,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Jintan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.00,Default,Jintan,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.27,0:15:53.47,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are your glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:55.93,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shut up! I can see fine without them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:58.25,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:15:59.10,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:03.11,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's really been a long time since the two of you have come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.11,0:16:05.81,Default,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you want to try the jelly Naruko made last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:08.65,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Do you still have some on Anaru's jelly left?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.24,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:13.85,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, getting the rare Nokemon is Menma's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:15.76,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, I told you not to talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:16.66,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.13,0:16:17.96,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Anaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:21.16,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, what was that about Menma?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:26.75,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,How do I say it... It's like she's been popping up in my dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:28.69,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Menma's has?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:33.86,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, Nokemon should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.86,0:16:35.24,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is it over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.24,0:16:38.05,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,No, those are my Love and Perry cards. {is this a reference to something?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.05,0:16:39.80,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,And that one's for Cow King.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.80,0:16:41.34,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Cow King? If you have that then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:43.82,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,We're looking for Nokemon, not Cow King.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:45.39,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Why haven't you joined us in her room?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:51.94,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Because when I'm around, both my mom and Anaru start feeling sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:52.54,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,That's Dojimon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.54,0:16:53.12,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Dojimon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.12,0:16:56.86,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing? We're searching for Nokemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:59.30,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, Nokemon, Nokemon, Nokemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:00.30,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Are you actually looking for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:01.40,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:02.80,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:02.78,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:04.62,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:07.99,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Bobobo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:08.84,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:14.05,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,You actually wrote your name on this little game?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:16.17,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,You were really thorough back then. {thorough -> methodical?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:17.20,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:31.58,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't read it in a while. Bobobo is so funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:34.97,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my gosh! I can't believe it, why don't I have Poitto?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:39.24,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, you have to trade rare Nokemon like Poison or Gangarga...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.58,0:17:41.95,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,You can't find Poison in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:43.51,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,You have to evolve him from Poitto.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:44.96,Default,Anal,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see yours real quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:50.39,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Anaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:52.20,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:55.23,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Anaru hasn't changed after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:59.55,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,She's kind, and she has lots of video games and manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:01.19,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,She's the same as she was back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:03.82,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:09.06,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,This feels nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.14,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.51,Default,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Menma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:40.20,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I got Poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:42.62,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Jintan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.83,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Anjou.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:55.69,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it. It helped me kill some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:59.21,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Do I get something for helping you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:00.92,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Like, money?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.92,0:19:02.41,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:07.62,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,Come to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:16.40,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,So, how's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:19.91,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:22.64,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Now we just connect the cable and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:35.23,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,There. Now I can trade with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:38.95,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Anjou?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:41.83,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,What? Oh, just a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:53.64,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:54.59,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,Nokemon-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.59,0:19:56.84,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta Catch 'em All!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:01.61,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you, Jintan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:02.53,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.15,0:20:09.76,Default,Anaru,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:14.50,Default,Poppo,0000,0000,0000,,This is great. Menma must be happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:15.97,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:26.46,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like that wasn't my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:27.80,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:30.40,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,But lots of nice things happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:33.98,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,You're friends with Anaru and Poppo again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:37.34,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,All you think of are other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:42.29,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.55,0:20:47.81,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:52.29,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, all I've done has all been fun. {rhymes, imitates Desu Yo's joke structure}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:54.11,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:56.11,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Desu Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:57.50,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.50,0:20:58.70,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:02.27,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,'Lately all I've done has all been fun.'
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.98,0:21:05.24,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've had fun in a while, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:07.33,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:10.20,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:18.36,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,The weather's nice today, and I had fun all day...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:15.99,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like my trauma isn't going away any time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.81,0:21:20.17,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,But as long as there's a tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:23.60,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I can take my time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:25.97,Default,Menma,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, yo, yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:25.98,Default,Jinta,0000,0000,0000,,...to apologize.
