Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:36.92,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,kaerimichi no kousaten de koe wo kaketekureta ne
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:39.69,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,"issho ni kaerou"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:48.19,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa terekusasou ni kaban de kao wo kakushinagara
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:53.78,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,hontou wa totemo totemo ureshikatta yo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:22:02.51,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,aa hanabi ga yozora kirei ni saite chotto setsunaku
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:09.19,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,aa kaze ga jikan to tomo ni nagareru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.64,0:22:16.87,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,ureshikute tanoshikute bouken mo iro iro shita ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:23.58,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,futari no himitsu no kichi no naka
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.88,0:22:30.88,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi to natsu no owari shourai no yume ookina kibou wasurenai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.88,0:22:37.84,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,jyuunen no ato hachigatsu mata deaeru no wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.07,0:22:45.17,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi ga saigo made kokoro kara "arigatou" sakendeita koto shitetayo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:52.16,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,namida wo koraete egao de sayounara setsunai yo ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:59.66,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,saikou no omoide wo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:30.14,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,We met in an unexpected moment
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:36.92,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,when you called out to me at the crosswalk,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:39.69,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's walk home together."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:48.19,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I might've hidden shyly behind my bag,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:53.78,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,but the truth is, I was really, really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:22:02.51,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks blossomed heartrendingly beautiful across the night sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.95,0:22:09.19,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,and time passed as swiftly as the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.64,0:22:16.87,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,We shared so many happy times and trilling adventures
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:23.58,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,together in our secret base.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.88,0:22:30.88,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never forget the hopes and dreams we shared during that one summer's end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.88,0:22:37.84,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we will meet again in another August, in maybe ten years time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.07,0:22:45.17,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,I could feel your heartfelt thanks all the way until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:52.16,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,And I know it must've been painful to hold back your tears and say goodbye with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.58,0:22:59.66,Ending 2,,0000,0000,0000,,But those are my best memories.
